Please follow contact.module.ts single entity.
Do not make migration file.
update package.json "migration:generate": "cross-env NODE_ENV=development ts-node -r tsconfig-paths/register ./node_modules/typeorm/cli.js migration:generate -d src/config/data-source.ts src/migrations/user-up",
this line if ever migration needed for example at the last of the line 'user-up' will update to 'contact-added' if i want to migrate contact entity.
use yarn migration:generate command to generate migration file.
use yarn migration:run command to run migration file.